d after:absolute after:w-12 text-3xl lg:text-4xl mb-8 after:-bottom-4 text-gray-100">Delivery</h2><p class="text-xl lg:text-2xl ">Delivery is the clean code and consistent design work we bring to our clients.</p></div><div class="grid lg:grid-cols-2 gap-4 lg:gap-8 items-center"><div><h3 class="after:left-0 font-semibold relative after:content[&quot;&quot;] after:h-1 after:rounded-full after:bg-brand after:absolute after:w-12, font-semibold relative after:content[&quot;&quot;] after:h-1 after:rounded-full after:bg-brand after:absolute after:w-12 text-xl lg:text-2xl mb-6 after:-bottom-2 text-gray-100">How We Deliver</h3><p class="text-lg mb-6">Vehikl acts as an extension of other development teams. We build best-in-class web applications with a strong focus on test-driven development.</p><p class="text-lg ">We collaborate with our clients and use Mob programming to deliver quality code at a consistent pace. Working as a team enables us to quickly remove bottlenecks and shorten the code review process. On a weekly basis, we focus on delivering features that provide business value to stakeholders.</p></div><div data-gatsby-image-wrapper="" class="gatsby-image-wrapper gatsby-image-wrapper-constrained mb-2 order-first"><div style="max-width:1385px;display:block"><img alt="" role="presentation" aria-hidden="true" src="data:image/svg+xml;charset=utf-8,%3Csvg height=&#x27;858&#x27; width=&#x27;1385&#x27; xmlns=&#x27;http://www.w3.org/2000/svg&#x27; version=&#x27;1.1&#x27;%3E%3C/svg%3E" style="max-width:100%;display:block;position:static"/></div><img aria-hidden="true" data-placeholder-image="" style="opacity:1;transition:opacity 500ms linear" decoding="async" src="data:image/png;base64," alt=""/><picture><source type="image/webp" srcSet="/static/62c71168236a37e74e1123499ed5cf8d/cdab2/code_delivery.webp 346w,/static/62c71168236a37e74e1123499ed5cf8d/13216/code_delivery.webp 693w,/static/62c71168236a37e74e1123499ed5cf8d/24bb8/code_delivery.webp 1385w" sizes="(min-width: 1385px)